findings.title: INITIAL_SUPPLY mismatch
findings.description: The INITIAL_SUPPLY in contract ASM has a value of 380831804 tokens, which differs from the white paper figure of 380831803.

findings.title: Insecure function name 'send()'
findings.description: The function name 'send()' can cause issues when using web3 or truffle to interact with the contract due to predefined send functions. It is recommended to rename it to 'sendTokens()'.
